name: Metaphys Tyrant Dragon
desc: If this card was Special Summoned by a "Metaphys" monster's effect, it is unaffected by Trap effects, also, if it attacks a monster, it can make a second attack in a row. Once per turn, during the Standby Phase, if this card was banished last turn: You can shuffle this banished card into the Deck; Special Summon 1 "Metaphys" monster from your hand, but banish it during the End Phase of the next turn.
